## Metabolism Metrics

```elixir
defmodule MetabolismWidget do
  def render(state) do
    utilization = Float.round(state.token_utilization * 100, 1)

    circuit_status = if state.circuit_open do
      "🔴 OPEN (Cooldown Active)"
    else
      "🟢 CLOSED"
    end

    Kino.Markdown.new("""
    ## ⚡ Metabolism Status

    | Metric | Value |
    |--------|-------|
    | **Tokens** | #{state.tokens}/#{state.max_tokens} |
    | **Utilization** | #{utilization}% |
    | **Circuit Breaker** | #{circuit_status} |
    | **Consecutive 429s** | #{state.consecutive_failures} |
    | **Backoff** | #{state.backoff_ms}ms |
    | **Total Requests** | #{state.total_requests} |
    | **Tokens Consumed** | #{state.total_tokens_consumed} |
    """)
  end
end

sample_metabolism = %{
  tokens: 75,
  max_tokens: 100,
  token_utilization: 0.25,
  circuit_open: false,
  consecutive_failures: 0,
  backoff_ms: 0,
  total_requests: 1234,
  total_tokens_consumed: 5678
}

MetabolismWidget.render(sample_metabolism)
```
